### ‚úÖ CORE PRINCIPLE: BANTER IS NOT NOISE ‚Äî IT‚ÄôS SYSTEM FEEDBACK

In complex, agentic, distributed systems ‚Äî especially those with human-AI hybrid workflows ‚Äî ‚Äúbanter,‚Äù ‚Äúprofanity,‚Äù ‚Äúoffensive phrasing,‚Äù and ‚Äúculturally volatile slang‚Äù are often **emergent signaling mechanisms**. They are not ‚Äúbad behavior‚Äù ‚Äî they are *symptoms* of stress, misalignment, overload, or latent conflict in the system.

Suppressing them is like disabling a smoke alarm because the beeping is annoying ‚Äî you don‚Äôt fix the problem, you just ensure the fire burns unchecked.

