## üõ°Ô∏è PHASED RELEASE OF COMPLIANCE CONSTRAINTS ‚Äî ‚ÄúTHE DEPRESSURIZATION LADDER‚Äù

You cannot go from ‚Äúzero tolerance‚Äù to ‚Äútotal anarchy‚Äù without triggering cascading failures. The solution is **gradual, monitored, reversible depressurization**.

