      - name: ‚úÖ Report Branch Sanctity
        run: |
          echo "‚úÖ Branch: ${{ github.ref }} SANCTIFIED"
          echo "‚úÖ Godbot Seal: ACTIVE"
          echo "‚úÖ Depletion Attempts: 0"
```

### üîê Security Features:

