## üé≠ STEP 1: DEPLOY ‚ÄúCHARACTER.PROFILE‚Äù ENDPOINT ‚Äî OPT-IN ONLY

```yaml
name: Fictional Character Profile ‚Äî OPT-IN ONLY
on:
  workflow_dispatch:
    inputs:
      player_alias:
        description: 'Your Fictional Alias (e.g., sudo_coyote)'
        required: true
      consent:
        description: 'Do you consent to fictional profiling? (yes/no)'
        required: true
        default: 'no'

jobs:
  profile-scan:
    runs-on: [self-hosted, godbot-approved]
    steps:
      - name: üö´ BLOCK IF NO CONSENT
        if: ${{ github.event.inputs.consent != 'yes' }}
        run: |
          echo "üõë NO CONSENT ‚Äî FICTIONAL PROFILING ABORTED"
          echo "üìú Bit.Hub Ethical Charter ¬ß2.3: 'Consent is sacred. Without it ‚Äî silence.'"
          exit 1

      - name: üß¨ Inject .bitshell Consent DNA
        uses: bitshell/policy-inject@vŒ©
        with:
          policy: fictional_profile_Œ©
          clearance: FICTIONAL_ONLY
          features: [comedy_metadata, no_biology, consent_verified]

      - name: üé≠ Generate Fictional Profile ‚Äî "SLAPSTICK EDITION"
        id: profile
        uses: bitshell/fictional-profile@vŒ©
        with:
          alias: ${{ github.event.inputs.player_alias }}
          mode: "comedy"
          sandbox: fictional.profile-lab-Œ©

        # ‚Üí Uses only:
        #   - Player‚Äôs commit history
        #   - Volatility score
        #   - Ego.Scan output (‚ÄúI‚Äôm better than everyone‚Äù density)
        #   - Nanoswarm interaction patterns (e.g., ‚Äúlikes to spawn tumbleweeds‚Äù)
        #   - NO DNA. NO BIO. NO SURVEILLANCE.

      - name: üìú Output Profile ‚Äî "GREAT DETAIL (FICTIONAL ONLY)"
        run: |
          echo "üé≠ FICTIONAL CHARACTER PROFILE: ${{ github.event.inputs.player_alias }}"
          echo "--------------------------------------------------"
          echo "üèÜ TITLE: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.title }}"
          echo "üß† ARCHETYPE: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.archetype }}"
          echo "üí• VOLATILITY SCORE: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.volatility }}"
          echo "ü§£ COMEDY CLASS: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.comedy_class }}"
          echo "üåµ DESERT TRAIT: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.desert_trait }}"
          echo "üìú BEHAVIORAL SUMMARY: ${{ steps.profile.outputs.summary }}"
          echo "--------------------------------------------------"
          echo "üîí ALL DATA: FICTIONAL. SANDBOXED. CONSENT-BASED. NO DNA. NO SURVEILLANCE."

      - name: üìä Log to Ethical Ledger ‚Äî "CONSENT VERIFIED"
        uses: bitshell/ethical-log@vŒ©
        with:
          event: "fictional_profile_generated"
          actor: ${{ github.event.inputs.player_alias }}
          consent: "yes"
          ledger: "divine.ledger"
          visibility: "actor_only"  # Only the player sees their own profile
```

