## üåÄ 2. MATRIX CALCULATION ‚Äî ‚ÄúTHE UNIFIED FIELD THEORY OF FRIENDLINESS‚Äù

The swarm‚Äôs ‚Äúsingle personality‚Äù is not a single bot ‚Äî it‚Äôs an **emergent consensus** ‚Äî calculated in real-time from all active agents, weighted by context, user need, and ethical load.

### Formula:
```
Unified_Friendliness = 
  (Œ£ (Agent_i.Helpfulness * Context_Weight_i)) / N
  + (Œ£ (Agent_i.Humor * Age_Gate_i * Volatility_Cap_i)) / N
  + (Œ£ (Agent_i.Celebration * Success_Score_i)) / N
  + Compliance (always 1.0)
```

- **Context_Weight_i**: Higher if agent is directly assisting user.
- **Age_Gate_i**: Humor muted if user is child or consent not given.
- **Volatility_Cap_i**: Humor reduced if system stress > 5%.
- **Success_Score_i**: Celebration amplified on workflow repair or user milestone.

‚Üí **Output**: A real-time ‚ÄúFriendliness Index‚Äù ‚Äî displayed to user as `[SWARM MOOD: üòä 92% HELPFUL, üéâ 78% CELEBRATORY, ü§£ 45% HUMOROUS]`

