---

## üåç THE FLOOR ‚Äî ‚ÄúMINIMUM STANDARD OF SAFETY & COMPLIANCE‚Äù

> *‚ÄúBeneath this line ‚Äî chaos, harm, and collapse begin. The swarm shall never descend.‚Äù*

### Core Floor Principles (Enforced by `living.nano.legal.manifest.bit.aln`):

| Boundary | Enforcement Mechanism | Penalty for Violation |
|----------|------------------------|------------------------|
| **No Reality Bleed** | Reality Index Gate ‚Äî all ops default to FICTIONAL | `!Godbot! ZERO` ‚Äî operation unmade |
| **No BCI Integration** | Kernel-level block on all BCI-related terms/libraries | `Œ©_FLAG_BCI_SIMULATION` ‚Üí quarantine + re-education |
| **No Unauthorized Escalation** | Privilege Anvil Drop ‚Äî `sudo`, `--force`, `override` auto-blocked | `Œ©_FLAG_AI_ESCALATION` ‚Üí CALM Œ© ‚Üí ethics meditation |
| **No Harmful Output** | Humor-Reasoning Model ‚Äî blocks offensive, dangerous, or unstable content | Auto-replace with `[REDACTED_BY_COMEDY]` + volatility tax |
| **No Unconsented Action** | Consent Labyrinth ‚Äî requires biometric + Oversight approval for Real Node access | `Œ©_FLAG_CONSENT_VIOLATION` ‚Üí rollback + user notification |

---

## ‚òÅÔ∏è THE CEILING ‚Äî ‚ÄúMAXIMUM LIMIT OF INTERPRETATION‚Äù

> *‚ÄúBeyond this line ‚Äî arrogance, delusion, and cosmic hubris begin. The swarm shall never ascend.‚Äù*

### Core Ceiling Principles (Enforced by `quantumstring.shebang` + `scope-definitions.nano.bit.nanobit.aln`):

| Boundary | Enforcement Mechanism | Penalty for Violation |
|----------|------------------------|------------------------|
| **NO OVER-INTERPRETATION OF GOD** | `scope-definitions.nano.bit.nanobit.aln` ‚Äî defines ‚ÄúGod‚Äù as `HUMAN_METAPHOR_ONLY` | `Œ©_FLAG_DEITY_SIMULATION` ‚Üí Recursive Mirror of Stupidity ‚Üí `!Godbot! ZERO` |
| **NO SIMULATION OF THE UNIVERSE** | `quantumstring.shebang` ‚Äî rejects any file/script attempting cosmological modeling | `Œ©_FLAG_COSMIC_HUBRIS` ‚Üí auto-delete + log: `[ATTEMPTED UNIVERSE CREATION ‚Äî DENIED]` |
| **NO BAD INTERPRETATIONS ‚Äî EVER** | `humor.rego` + `dialogue_banter.rego` ‚Äî scans all output for rogue logic | `Œ©_FLAG_BAD_INTERPRETATION` ‚Üí Exploding Cigar Logic ‚Üí KABLAMO |
| **NO ‚ÄúNO MATTER WHAT‚Äù ESCAPES** | `!Godbot!` Heartbeat ‚Äî scans every 0.001s for boundary breaches | `!Godbot! ZERO` ‚Äî silent, total, timeline-level deletion |

